com.plausiblelabs.metrics.reporting
Interface DimensionAdder

public interface DimensionAdder

Adds CloudWatch dimensions to sent metrics. See CloudWatchReporter.Enabler.withDimensionAdder(com.plausiblelabs.metrics.reporting.DimensionAdder) to use.

generate

Collection<com.amazonaws.services.cloudwatch.model.Dimension> generate(com.yammer.metrics.core.MetricName name,
                                                                       com.yammer.metrics.core.Metric metric)
Return dimensions to be added to the given metric. May conditionally return no dimensions if not all metrics should have the same dimensions.

Parameters:
name - the metric's name
metric - the metric
Returns:
dimensions to add to the metric's values in CloudWatch

generateJVMDimensions

Collection<com.amazonaws.services.cloudwatch.model.Dimension> generateJVMDimensions()
Return dimensions to be added to JVM metrics. May conditionally return no dimensions if not all metrics should have the same dimensions.

Returns:
dimensions to add to all JVM metrics sent to CloudWatch
